<div id="training" class="form-step  hidden">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">LEARNING AND DEVELOPMENT / TRAININGS</h2>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 mt-4 mb-4">*If all fields in a row are not applicable, enter 'N/A' in one of the fields within that row.</h4>
        <section class="bg-white p-4 rounded-md">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Learning and Development Interventions</h3>
          <ul class="text-xs list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>
              Indicate <strong>FULL titles</strong> of learning and development (L&amp;D) interventions attended during employment. 
              Indicate list from the most recent L&amp;D.
            </li>
            <li>
              Indicate the <strong>type</strong> of L&amp;D intervention (e.g. managerial, supervisory, technical).
            </li>
            <li>
              Indicate the <strong>FULL name</strong> of institution/agency that conducted or sponsored the program. 
              <strong>DO NOT ABBREVIATE.</strong> (e.g. CSC should be Civil Service Commission).
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

